    <metadata>
      <schema>http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM</schema>
      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">
        <general>
          <identifier>
            <catalog>oercommons.org</catalog>
            <entry>1770211558</entry>
          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">The Photoelectric Effect</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Der Photoelektrische Effekt</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">l'Effet Photoélectrique</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">O Efeito Fotoelétrico</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">L'Effetto Fotoelettrico</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Η φωτοηλεκτρική επίδραση</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El Efecto Fotoeléctrico</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">See how light knocks electrons off a metal target, and recreate the experiment that spawned the field of quantum mechanics. </string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Science and Technology</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <language>es</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sehen Sie, wie Licht Elektronen weg von einem 
Metallziel klopft, und erstellen Sie das Experiment neu, das 
auffangene der Quantummechaniker laichte.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Voyez comment la lumière frappe des électrons 
outre d'une cible en métal, et recréez l'expérience qui a engendré
la zone de la mécanique quantique.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Veja como a luz bate elétrons fora de um alvo do 
metal, e recreie a experiência que spawned o campo de mecânicos do 
quantum.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Veda come la luce batte gli elettroni fuori di un 
obiettivo del metallo e ricrei l'esperimento che ha deposto le uova il
campo dei meccanici di quantum.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Δείτε πώς τα ελαφριά ηλεκτρόνια κτύπων από
ένα μέταλλο στοχεύουν, και αναδημιουργήστε το πείραμα που 
ωοτόκησε το πεδίο των κβαντικών μηχανικών.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Vea cómo la luz golpea electrones de una blanco 
del metal, y reconstruya el experimento que spawn/generó el campo de 
los mecánicos del quántum.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Wissenschaft und Technologie</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">La Science et technologie</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Ciência e tecnologia</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>

          </keyword>
          <keyword>
